"Rasta":
"This is Rasta, come in.
...Ah, I got through."
"Ratel and Rooikat returned just a moment ago. They're both safe and sound."
"Hey, sorry about all that. Rooikat went back to the city ahead of me."
"Man, he had you out looking for me? My bad! I didn't think they'd sent out the cavalry just cause I went home early."
"I'm sorry for putting you through so much trouble. Everything seems to be fine now, so please return as soon as you can."
